                               Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Inspired by such camp classics as THE EVIL DEAD, this outrageous horror film takes a bloody
tongue-in-cheek stab at the zombie genre. When an FBI-bred virus accidentally contaminates 
a small town, it turns its victims into the flesh-eating living dead. Quarantined from the rest of 
society, the zombies and the few souls they have yet to claim (led by pro wrestler John West 
and medical student Max Griggs) fight to find the map that reveals an exit to safety.
